<p>While working on many scientific and philosophical problems, dear Prof. Fang likes to have a nice cup of tea and a couple of biscuits.</p>
<p>She wants to track how many biscuits she eats depending on the cups of tea.</p>
<p>Each day for a week she writes down how many cups of tea she drank and how many tasty biscuits.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>


